The titlescreen...
   There are some thing for You to select here.
Use <arrow down> to move down, and <arrow up> to move up. Use 
<arrow left> to scroll item left, and <arrow right> to scroll ri-
ght. Press <Return> to confirm.
   Start Game...   - Start game.
   Level: 1-10   - Select level to start at.
   Mode: 1-3   - Difficult of game (eg. speed), low-fast.
   Controll: Mouse/Joy 1 - Controll of game.
   MusicVolume: 0-4   - 0 for no music.
   Hiscore...   - View hiscore.
   Clear Hiscore...   - Will let You erase all saved scores.
   Info...   - Short information about the game.
   Exit...   - Quit to workbench/CLI.

-----------------------------------------------------------------

The game...
   Movebat up or Down   - Mouse/joy up or down.
   Shoot ball away   - Left mouse-button/left-joy/right-joy.

There is a row of icons on a lower screen. An arrow will move
from left to right as You destroy the bricks. If You want the se-
lected item, press right mouse-button  or fire - the arrow will 
then start from absolute left again.
   'X' - Nothing.
   Empty - Set bonus-used to absolutely nothing. Sometimes you 
           can get pretty tired of 'Glue'...
   'LessSpeed' - Makes the ball move slower.
   'Glue' - Ball will stick to bat on hit, and you may aim a
            little better.
   'ShowInv.' - Show invisible blocks.
   'ShowBns.' - Show bonuses, hidden in blocks.
   'KillHard' - Lets your ball destroy what can not be destroyed.
   'ShowPIV' - Shows where the PIV block is hidden.
   'OneHit' - Lets your ball destroy blocks with one hit.
   'HardBall' - Your ball will continue in the same direction 
                even if it hits a visible block.
   'PIV' - Complete level without finding the PIV-block.
   '2000' - That's loads of score!

There are many bonuses hidden under the default blocks, and they
will appear as the blocks goes to destruction.
   'PIV' - This is what you are searching for!
   'S' - Slowdown ball.
   '1' - Bonus marker will jump one step forward.
   '2' - Bonus marker will jump two steps forward.
   BlueWithSomeLinesOn - Ball will go faster (not good...)
   GoldenWithBlackBar - Ball will be teleported to bat.
   '1UP' - Extra life.
   '100' - 100 points added to score.
   '500' - 500 points added to score.

Game keys:
   'P' - Pause/unpause.
   'Esc' - Game over!

-----------------------------------------------------------------

Installing new levels...
   Visit your local level-installer!.. or just put the new levels
in the data-drawer ;)   If you don't want to erase your old
levels, you'll have to rename the new ones.
   The first level must be named '1.LVL', the second '2.LVL'
a.s.o.   But remember that this version can't carry more than
8 of them!

